{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/2023-02-28-practical-shell-script-snippets/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Beveloper","heroImage":"/images/beveloper-hero.jpg"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c136a23a-ab19-5a10-a7d5-d39fc30c9415","excerpt":"Create private key + public key, then display public key","html":"<h1>Create private key + public key, then display public key</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">key_name</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"my-server-key\"</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># How to name your key pair?</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">key_path</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"~/.ssh\"</span>         <span class=\"token comment\"># Where to store your key pair?</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">passphrase</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>             <span class=\"token comment\"># Password of your key pair. \"\" means no password.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-n</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$key_name</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> ssh-keygen <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-t</span> rsa <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-C</span> <span class=\"token variable\">${key_name}</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-N</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\">$key_pair_for_web_ins_passphrase</span>\"</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-f</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$key_path</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">${key_name}</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> <span class=\"token number\">400</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$key_path</span>/<span class=\"token variable\">${key_name}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Practical Shell Script Snippets","date":"2023-02-28T01:00:00+00:00","description":"During development work, created some very useful shell script snippets.","featuredImageUrl":"https://d1m75rqqgidzqn.cloudfront.net/wp-data/2021/06/11162836/iStock-1313617131.jpg"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2023-03-10-deta-space-fastapi-flutter-web-xmlhttprequest-pitfall/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Deta Space + FastAPI + Flutter Web: XMLHttpRequest Pitfall"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2023-02-28-practical-aws-cli-examples/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Practical AWS CLI Examples"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"c136a23a-ab19-5a10-a7d5-d39fc30c9415","previousPostId":"fb9fcec2-2353-5d5e-aacb-aec2937a2f4c","nextPostId":"43971360-944e-5840-859f-7a4d02db93cd"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1261413882","2660733687"]}